content: Dutch synchronized swimmer **Catrien Eijken** (born 29 June 1961) is a former [synchronized swimmer](/wiki/Synchronized_swimming) from [The Netherlands](/wiki/Netherlands). She competed in both the [women's solo](/wiki/Synchronized_swimming_at_the_1984_Summer_Olympics_%E2%80%93_Women%27s_solo) and the [women's duet](/wiki/Synchronized_swimming_at_the_1984_Summer_Olympics_%E2%80%93_Women%27s_duet) competitions at the [1984 Summer Olympics](/wiki/1984_Summer_Olympics).
